metadata.name: Spaghettified - David Jones x Landlinesart
metadata.description:
A poem by David Jones, transposed onto a Landlinesart piece of generative art.  Created by Greg Younger.

"My heart is wrapped in  
Spaghettified spacetime,  
Criss-crossed with a million lives:  
Lived, imagined, dreamed -  
Loves, losses -  
Tangled in singularity."
